    rdfs:label "Tahmuras Defeats the Divs"@en, "هزيمت ديوها به دست طهمورث"@fa;
    rdfs:comment "Tahmuras, shown here galloping across a meadow, defeated the divs (demons), in exchange for their lives, they taught him the art of writing. This work is attributed to Sultan Muhammad, the master painter and chief administrator of the first generation of artists of this manuscript"@en;
